    "description": "<span></span><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Intro</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">What Are We Up To?</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">C: Nobody, Boba Fett, Peacemaker, The Eternals, Yakuza: Like a Dragon, A Short Hike, Mom Hid My Game</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">T: Fellowship of the Ring Part 1, lots of Seinfeld, Civ VI, Kingdom Two Crowns: Norselands, more Mario Party Superstar, store shelf watching</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">B: Halo Infinite, Masterchief Collection, books, SNOW!</span></p></li></ul></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Brandon\u2019s Random Factoid</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Assholes of the Week: </span><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/19/1073908955/senate-voting-rights-bills-filibuster\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Senate GOP with the help of Manchin & Sinema blocked the Dems from changing the filibuster to get voting rights bills up for vote</span></a></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/19/1074071024/university-michigan-sexual-abuse-sports-doctor\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">University of Michigan reached a $490 million settlement over sexual abuse by former sports doctor</span></a></p></li></ul></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Heroes of the Week: </span><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/19/1074226489/the-supreme-court-denies-trumps-bid-to-block-release-of-records-to-jan-6-panel\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">SCOTUS denies Trump\u2019s request to block the release of White House records to the January 6 panel</span></a><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">, </span><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/18/1073898495/jan-6-panel-subpoenas-rudy-giuliani-other-lawyers-tied-to-false-election-claims\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">January 6 committee sent out subpoenas for Rudy Giuliani and the other Trump lawyers that tried to overturn the election</span></a></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/19/1074000357/new-yorks-attorney-general-says-trumps-company-misled-banks-tax-officials\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">NY AG seeks to question Trump, Ivanka and Don Jr. over uncovered evidence of fraud/misleading asset valuations</span></a></p></li></ul></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/louie-anderson-dead-comedian-baskets-star-1235078681/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">RIP Louie Anderson</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">COVID Dump Truck</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/18/1073817562/order-covid-tests-free-biden-white-house\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The USPS is taking orders for free at-home COVID test kits</span></a><span style=\"font-size:11pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">, </span><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/21/1074815001/free-covid-test-kits-phone-number\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Plus a phone line</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/19/1074037421/the-biden-administration-will-give-out-400-million-free-n95-masks\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">400 million N95 face masks will be given out for free through pharmacies</span></a></p></li></ul></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/18/1073857310/tesla-autopilot-crash-charges\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Tesla driver whose car ran a red light and hit a car, killing two people, has been charged</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/21/1074733306/intel-ohio-computer-chips\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Intel announced a $20 billion investment to build chip facility in Ohio</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/17/1073586705/winter-storm-could-drop-foot-of-snow-on-northeast\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">A huge winter storm wreaked havoc on the eastern US from the south to the northeast</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2022/01/18/1073800454/nasa-scientists-estimate-tonga-blast-at-10-megatons\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">NASA estimates that the Tonga volcanic explosion was around 10 megatons</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://variety.com/2022/tv/news/lord-of-the-rings-rings-of-power-amazon-series-1235156784/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power is the name of the upcoming Amazon series</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://variety.com/2022/digital/news/squid-game-season-2-netflix-confirms-1235159078/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Squid Game will get a second season at Netflix</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://variety.com/2022/tv/news/nicole-byer-lauren-lapkus-netflix-bad-crimes-mike-judge-greg-daniels-1235156215/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Netflix orders animated comedy series Bad Crimes for a 10 episode series</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://variety.com/2022/film/news/daniel-radcliffe-weird-al-yankovic-movie-1235156084/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Weird Al is getting an original biopic movie with Roku</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://variety.com/2022/film/news/bong-joon-ho-movie-robert-pattinson-warner-bros-1235157577/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Bong Joon Ho\u2019s next film will be an adaptation of an upcoming sci-fi novel</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x7Krla_UxRg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">A trailer for The Moon Knight Disney+ series</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pldV6eZdHWo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">A trailer for Shenmue the Animation ahead of its February 5 debut</span></a></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sel3fjl6uyo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">A trailer for The Cuphead Show on Netflix that will be out February 18</span></a></p></li></ul><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Contact us at </span><a href=\"mailto:letsweekenders@gmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">letsweekenders@gmail.com</span></a>",
